ons like legal document analysis, scientific argument mining, and educational feedback systems, where interpretability and accuracy are paramount. Unlike prior work that treats transfer learning as static initialization or multi-task training, our method uses auxiliary knowledge *dynamically during inference*, making it adaptive and context-sensitive.",
